                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="right-image col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mobile-bottom-fix-big"
                data-scroll-reveal="enter right move 30px over 0.6s after 0.4s">
                <img src="~/img/SmallAboutFish.jpg" class="rounded img-fluid d-block mx-auto" alt="App">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="hr"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="products-container">
    <img src="~/img/mainPage/779.jpg" class="products-under-img" />
    <h1 class="products-container-title">Хіт продажів</h1>
    <div class="products-container-view">
        <div class="products-container-view-info">
            <h2>Дорадо</h2>
            <p>Це м'ясо корисно для людей які мають проблеми з щитовидною залозою і бал бла бал...</p>
            <div class="products-container-view-info-read">
                <div class="products-details">
                    <p>27г білків</p>
                    <p>100 ккал</p>
                    <p>280грн/кг</p>
                </div>
                <form class="">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-add">
                        Добавити в корзину<span class="iconify btn-add-content" data-inline="false"
                            data-icon="akar-icons:plus"></span>
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="products-container-view-img">
            <div class="img-container">
                <img class="fish-img" src="~/img/mainPage/None_bgFish.png" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="products-container-preview">
        <div class="products-container-preview-controll">
            <div class="products-container-preview-controll-block">
                <button class="btn-previous" data-trigger="previous">
                    <span class="arrow arrow-left" data-trigger="previous"></span>
                </button>
                <h3>1/1</h3>
                <button class="btn-next" data-trigger="next">
                    <span class="arrow arrow-right" data-trigger="next"></span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="products-container-preview-other">
            @foreach (var p in Model)
            {
                <div class="product-card">
                    <img src="~/images/productsImages/@p.Image" class="product-card-img" />
                    <div class="product-card-titleAndinfo">
                        <h5>@p.ProductName</h5>
                        <p>@p.PricePerKg грн/кг</p>
                        <div>
                            <form class="">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn-add">
                                    <span class="iconify btn-add-content" data-inline="false"
                                        data-icon="akar-icons:plus"></span>
                                </button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="contacts-container" id="contact">
    <div class="contacts-container-info">
        <h4>Ми завжди на зв'язку</h4>
        <p>
            Якщо у вас виникли якісь питання, ми завжди будемо раді відповісти на них, при потребІ, допомогти з вибором
            товару.
        </p>
        <h3>тел. +380 896 338 137</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="contacts-container-logo">
        <object data="~/img/mainPage/ContactLogo.svg" type="image/svg+xml" class="contact-logo"></object>
    </div>
</div>


<script src="https://code.iconify.design/1/1.0.6/iconify.min.js"></script> 
<script src="~/js/Products/productCard.js"></script>